   Generation for seed 1942 failed:
   While parsing file "/dev/stdin", line 10: 
   While parsing posting:
     (mc48XU1x:96dQzRe)  -1e+06 SLKn
                         ^^^^^^^^^^^
   Error: Unexpected char '+' (Note: inline math requires parentheses)
   :END:
