   [2009-03-01 Sun 01:08]
** DEFERRED [[bug:259][#259]] Look at making ledger's new entry completion behavior cyclic
   - State "DEFERRED"   from "TODO"       [2009-10-25 Sun 22:04]
   :PROPERTIES:
